longBusinessSummary: Wilton Resources Corporation Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the exploration, mining, and production of gold ores and gold dore. It holds an interest in the Ciemas gold project covering a total area of 3,078.5 hectares located in West Java, Indonesia. The company is also involved in general trading, transportation, construction, real estate, logging, farming, plantation, forestry, electrical, mechanical, computer, workshop, and printing and services businesses. It operates in Indonesia and Singapore. The company is based in Singapore.
